  "prompt": "Has Jay-Z ever performed together live with Panjabi MC and/or Labh Janjua?",
  "response": "Jay-Z has performed live with Panjabi MC. The most notable collaboration between them is the remix of Panjabi MC's hit song \"Mundian To Bach Ke,\" which features Jay-Z. This remix includes Jay-Z's rap verses and was released in the early 2000s. They have performed this version live together on several occasions.\n\nAs for Labh Janjua, there is no widely known record of Jay-Z having performed live with him. Labh Janjua was an Indian singer known for popular tracks like \"Mundian To Bach Ke\" and \"Jee Karda,\" but collaborations and live performances with Jay-Z are not documented.",
